{"content": "I need to multiply 772 \u00d7 858 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 772\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 567 + 63 + 2 = 632\u2081\u2080\n- 858\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 648 + 45 + 8 = 701\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 632 \u00d7 701 = 443,032\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 443032 \u00f7 9 = 49225 r 7\n- 49225 \u00f7 9 = 5469 r 4\n- 5469 \u00f7 9 = 607 r 6\n- 607 \u00f7 9 = 67 r 4\n- 67 \u00f7 9 = 7 r 4\n- 7 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 7\n\nReading from bottom to top: **744647\u2089**\n\n744647", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}